data.description: Hard to find hillside view lot in the heart of Ventura. Over 100 avocado trees included. Lot is located south of 1678 Buena Vista from the sign all the way down to the end of white split rail fence. Soil & geological have been completed. Water meter will be provided by close of escrow. Gas and power are in the street. We have Topo map and copy of soils report for property. Beautiful views of the ocean and the mountains above. Very expensive homes in the neighborhood.
